quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Nested if Statements[/h1]

You can use one [b]if-else[/b] statement inside another[b] if[/b] or [b]else [/b]statement.
[b]For example:[/b] [code format="java" codeId="729"]int age = 25;
if(age > 0) {
   if(age > 16) {
      System.out.println("Welcome!");
   } else {
      System.out.println("Too Young");
   }
} else {
   System.out.println("Error");
}
//Outputs "Welcome!"[/code]
[note]You can nest as many [b]if-else[/b] statements as you want.[/note]
